original: Håkansson, Herman Ludvig, landskanslist, Karlskrona, f. 21/11/91 i Karlskrona. G. 41 m. Ebba Qvarlan-der. — Länsmansex. 12. Landskanslist sed. 22, kommissionär h. länsstyr. i Blek. län.
translated: Håkansson, Herman Ludvig, a civil servant in the County Administrative Board, Karlskrona, born on November 21, 1891 in Karlskrona. Married in 1941 to Ebba Qvarlander. He worked as a constable from 1912 and as a civil servant since 1922. He was a commissioner in the county administrative board of Blekinge county.

employer.name: County Administrative Board of Blekinge county
